Included page: .ScenarioLibrary (edit)

These scenarios will be accessible to all test cases in the the FitNesseRoot folder. If you are using a different FitNesseRoot Folder, make sure to copy these files if using any setup scenarios.


Update these variables for your specific test environment


  • Expand

Variables for Scenarios

Default browser can be FIREFOX or CHROME
variable defined: defaultBrowser=FIREFOX

Default Version can be any supported Appian Version in xx.x format from (21.2 - 23.1)
variable defined: defaultVersion=23.1

Default Locale can be en_US or en_GB
variable defined: defaultLocale=en_US

Default URL should include http or https and /suite (e.g. https://forum.appian.com/suite )
variable defined: defaultUrl=REPLACE_APPIAN_URL

To use out of the box functionality, do not update the scenarios below

FitNesse Configurations


variable defined: TEST_SYSTEM=slim
variable defined: COMMAND_PATTERN=java -Dlog4j.configuration=file:///${automated.testing.home}/log4j.properties -cp %p %m
classpath: C:\Fitnesse/**.jar

Please follow the directions below to execute the test


  1. If your TESTING_HOME is located somewhere other than C:\Fitnesse, update automated.testing.home in TESTING_HOME/configs/custom.properties
    • For more information look at Changing FitNesse for Appian installation directory.
  2. Click "Edit" at the top of this page and update the following fields in the "Initialization and Login" block below
    • Replace APPIAN_URL with Appian URL, beginning with https:// and including /suite at the end (e.g. https://forum.appian.com/suite)
    • Replace APPIAN_VERSION with a supported version from (21.2 - 23.1)
    • Replace APPIAN_LOCALE with (en_US or en_GB) to handle differences in how dates are displayed
    • Replace APPIAN_USERNAME with a valid username for Appian URL above
    • Open C:\Fitnesse/configs/users.properties and add a line for the above username that is of the form username=password (e.g. test.user=password)
  3. Click "Test" at the top of this page

Populate fields


script
click on menu ORDER PARTS
wait for 5 seconds
take screenshot emptyform
click on checkbox option [1]
populate field Product Group with value Gops
$pg<-[Gops] get field Product Group value
click on radio option 1020
$plantgrp<-[1020] get field Plant Group value
click on radio option 630100
$gla<-[630100] get field GL Account value
populate field IO with 3 partially matching picker field suggestion
$io<-[IO123407] get field IO value
populate field CC with 2 partially matching picker field suggestion
$cc<-[CC002] get field CC value
populate field Short Order Description with value TEST SHORT ORDER DESC
$sodesc<-[TEST SHORT ORDER DESC] get field Short Order Description value
click on checkbox option [2]
click on checkbox option [3]
click on checkbox option [4]
populate field Deliver To with tv!location.delivery
populate field Building with tv!location.building
populate field Cube/Office/Lab Location with tv!location.ofc
populate grid [1] column Part Number row [1] with NPN
$pn<-[NPN] get grid [1] column Part Number row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Description row [1] with SERVICE SPARE PARTS PA_2IEIE32
$desc<-[SERVICE SPARE PARTS PA_2IEIE32] get grid [1] column Description row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Commodity row [1] with OTHER
$comm<-[OTHER] get grid [1] column Commodity row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Std Cost row [1] with 1000
$stdcost<-[1000] get grid [1] column Std Cost row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Qty row [1] with 2
$qty<-[2] get grid [1] column Qty row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Need Date row [1] with 04/20/2023
populate grid [1] column Addtl. Fee row [1] with 500
$addfee<-[500] get grid [1] column Addtl. Fee row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Delivery Type row [1] with Stock
$delivery<-[Stock] get grid [1] column Delivery Type row [1] value
populate grid [1] column Cust. Ship row [1] with value
populate grid [1] column Critical row [1] with value
populate grid [1] column RPM row [1] with value
take screenshot filledform
click on button PROCEED TO CHECKOUT
take screenshot confirmationscreen
click on button OK
